 Morley (Breconshire MP)|Morley]]\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Sidney Robinson (politician)|Robinson]]\n|}\n\n===1918 to 1983===\n{{legend2|{{Coalition Liberal/meta/color}}|[[Coalition Liberal]] (1918\u201322) / [[National Liberal Party (UK, 1922)|National Liberal]] (1922\u201323)|border=1px solid #aaaaaa}}\n{{legend2|{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}|[[Conservative Party (UK)|Conservative]]|border=1px solid #aaaaaa}}\n{{legend2|{{Independent (politician)/meta/color}}|[[Independent (politician)|Independent]]|border=1px solid #aaaaaa}}\n{{legend2|{{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}|[[Labour Party (UK)|Labour]]|border=1px solid #aaaaaa}}\n{{legend2|{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}|[[Liberal Party (UK)|Liberal]]|border=1px solid #aaaaaa}}\n{{legend2|{{National Government (United Kingdom)/meta/color}}|[[National Government (United Kingdom)|National Government]]|border=1px solid #aaaaaa}}\n{{legend2|{{National Liberal Party (UK, 1931)/meta/color}}|[[National Liberal Party (UK, 1931)|National Liberal]] (1931\u201368)|border=1px solid #aaaaaa}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Constituency\n!1918\n!1922\n!1923\n!1924\n!1929\n!''31''\n!1931\n!1935\n!''39''\n!''42''\n!1945\n!1950\n!1951\n!1955\n!1959\n!''62''\n!1964\n!1966\n!1970\n!Feb 1974\n!Oct 1974\n!1979\n|-\n|[[Montgomeryshire (UK Parliament constituency)|Montgomeryshire]]\n| colspan=\"4\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[David Davies, 1st Baron Davies|D. Davies]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Clement Davies|C. Davies]]\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{National Liberal Party (UK, 1931)/meta/color}}\"|[[Clement Davies|\u2192]]\n|bgcolor=\"{{Independent (politician)/meta/color}}\"|[[Clement Davies|\u2192]]\n| colspan=\"6\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\"|[[Clement Davies|\u2192]]\n| colspan=\"6\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\"|[[Emlyn Hooson, Baron Hooson|Hooson]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Delwy