{"title_page": "Home (2020 TV series)", "text_new": "{{Infobox television\n|show_name          = Home\n| image             = \n| image_size        = \n| genre             = [[Documentary television|Docuseries]]\n| creator           = \n| based_on          = \n| director          = {{Plainlist|\n* [[Matt Tyrnauer]]\n* Doug Pray\n* Taimi Arvidson\n* Jessica Dimmock\n* Scott Weintrob\n* Clay Jeter\n* Jimmy Goldblum \n}}\n| writer            = \n| story             = \n| starring          = \n| composer          =\n| country           = United States\n| language          = English\n| num_seasons       =\n| num_episodes      =\n| list_episodes     = #Episodes\n| executive_producer ={{Plainlist|\n* Matthew Weaver\n* Joe Poulin\n* Doug Pray \n* Ian Orefice\n* Bruce Gersh\n* Matt Tyrnauer\n* Corey Reeser\n* Collin Orcutt\n* Kim Rozenfeld\n}}\n| cinematography =\n| editor = \n| camera =\n| runtime =\n| channel = \n| picture_format = \n| audio_format = \n| company = {{Plainlist|\n* Media Weaver Entertainment\n* Four M Studios\n* Altimeter Films\n}}\n| distributor = [[Apple Inc.]]\n| network = [[Apple TV+]]\n| first_aired = \n| last_aired = \n| website = \n| related =\n| website_title =\n}}\n'''''Home''''' is an American [[Documentary television|documentary]] [[web television]] series produced for [[Apple TV+]]. In January 2018, Apple gave the production a series order consisting of a single season of nine episodes. Home, from MediaWeaver, Four M Studios and Altimeter Films, will premiere April 17, 2020. <ref>{{cite press release |url=https://apple-tv-plus-press.apple.com/en-US/news/2020/01/new-documentary-series-home-to-premiere-april-17-on-apple-tv/ |title=New documentary series \u201cHome\u201d to premiere April 17 on Apple TV+ |date=January 19, 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Premise==\n''Home'' guides the audience \"inside the world\u2019s most extraordinary homes and unveils the boundary-pushing imagination of the visionaries who dared to dream and build them.\"<ref name=\"SeriesOrder\">{{cite web|last1=Andreeva|first1=Nellie|title=Apple Orders \u2018Home\u2019 Docuseries From Matt Tyrnauer & Matthew Weaver|url=https://deadline.com/2018/01/apple-straight-to-series-order-home-docuseries-matt-tyrnauer-matthew-weaver-time-inc-productions-1202236235/|website=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|accessdate=February 19, 2018|date=January 5, 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Production==\nHome is executive produced by Joe Poulin, Matthew Weaver, Bruce Gersh, Ian Orefice, Doug Pray, Collin Orcutt, [[Matt Tyrnauer]], Corey Reeser and Kim Rozenfeld. Nick Stern serves as co-executive producer.<ref name=\"SeriesOrder\"/><ref>{{cite web|last1=Otterson|first1=Joe|title=Apple Orders Docuseries \u2018Home\u2019 Straight to Series|url=https://variety.com/2018/tv/news/apple-docuseries-home-1202654252/|website=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=February 19, 2018|date=January 5, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Freeman|first1=Luria|title=Apple's first docuseries 'Home' will explore lavish residences around the world|url=https://ew.com/tv/2018/01/05/apple-docuseries-home/|website=[[Entertainment Weekly]]|accessdate=February 19, 2018|language=en|date=January 5, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Goldberg|first1=Lesley|title=Apple Orders Its First Docuseries: Real Estate Entry 'Home'|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/apple-orders-first-docuseries-real-estate-entry-home-1071806|website=[[The Hollywood Reporter]]|accessdate=February 19, 2018|language=en|date=January 5, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Perez|first1=Sarah|title=Apple adds a documentary series about extraordinary homes to its streaming lineup|url=https://techcrunch.com/2018/01/05/apple-adds-a-documentary-series-about-extraordinary-homes-to-its-streaming-lineup/|website=[[TechCrunch]]|accessdate=February 19, 2018|language=en|date=January 5, 2018}}</ref> Matt Tyrnauer is set to direct the series.<ref name=\"SeriesOrder\"/>\n\n==Episodes==\n{{Episode table |total_width= |background=#000000 |overall= |title= |director