oogle.com/books?id=9GvpCQAAQBAJ }}\n* {{cite book |last=Randall |first=William Sterne |title=Alexander Hamilton: A Life |publisher=[[HarperCollins]] |isbn=978-0-0620-1532-7 |year=2015 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=2Ie3gYY8HacC |ref=randall}}\n* {{cite book |last=Schachner |first=Nathan |title=Alexander Hamilton |publisher=D. Appleton Century Co |location=New York City|asin=B0006AQUG2 |year=1946}}\n{{refend}}\n\n===Specialized studies===\n\n{{refbegin}}\n* {{cite journal |last=Adair |first=Douglas |lastauthoramp=yes |first2=Marvin |last2=Harvey |title=Was Alexander Hamilton a Christian Statesman? |journal=William and Mary Quarterly |volume=12 |issue=2 |year=1955 |pages=308\u201329 |doi=10.2307/1920511 |jstor=1920511 }}\n* {{cite book |last=Austin |first=Ian Patrick |title=Common Foundations of American and East Asian Modernisation: From Alexander Hamilton to Junichero Koizumi |location=Singapore |publisher=Select Books |year=2009 |url=https://books.google.com/?id=Rmg3gNJ5L44C&pg=PR7 |isbn=978-981-4022-52-1}}\n* {{cite journal |last=Bailey |first=Jeremy D. |title=The New Unitary Executive and Democratic Theory: The Problem of Alexander Hamilton |journal=[[American Political Science Review]] |year=2008 |volume=102 |issue=4 |pages=453\u201365 |doi=10.1017/S0003055408080337 |url=https://zenodo.org/record/894750/files/article.pdf }}\n* Balogh, Brian. 2009. ''A Government out of Sight: The Mystery of National Authority in Nineteenth Century American''. New York: Cambridge University Press.\n* Bordewich, Fergus M. ''The First Congress: How James Madison, George Washington, and a Group of Extraordinary Men Invented the Government'' (2016) on 1789\u201391.\n* {{cite book |last=Brant |first=Irving |title=The Fourth President: a Life of James Madison |location=Indianapolis |publisher=Bobbs-Merill |year=1970 |isbn=}} A one-volume recasting of Brant's six-volume life.\n* {{cite book |last=Burns |first=Eric |title=Infamous Scribblers: The Founding Fathers and the Rowdy Be